data.description: Paradise on an Island in SW Florida.  Situated on a generous half-acre lot, this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home offers the perfect blend of Island living and natural beauty.  Stunning landscaping surrounds the home with tropical foliage and vibrant bursts of color.  The interior of this home offers an open-concept that seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas.  Three spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space, tile floors throughout the entire home, this meticulously maintained home leaves no detail overturned.  The paver pool area is completely screened in and allows the inside to seamlessly flow outside.  New roof in 2020.  An additional ½ acre parcel is available for purchase if you desire even more privacy (MLS#223039019).  Whether lounging by the pool or enjoying a peaceful evening on the patio, you have found your private oasis.
